{"tid":2077123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.1遊行七方案 警充耳不聞  民陣：佢哋筆記都冇做 100%唔會批","createTime":"2020-06-24T05:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T10:18:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"904475404b6420eeb855d6bd0135cafe2c3c982c","tid":2077123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:05:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/OGYMKSXVHG6643DQXWHGJMBGHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FOGYMKSXVHG6643DQXWHGJMBGHA%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=22dd9791\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FOGYMKSXVHG6643DQXWHGJMBGHA%2F&h=ff6f9e34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/OGYMKSXVHG6643DQXWHGJMBGHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n7.1遊行七方案 警充耳不聞 <br />\n民陣：佢哋筆記都冇做 100%唔會批<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【惡法臨城】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民陣計劃發起下星期三的7.1遊行，林鄭政府以疫情為由，將限聚令延至7月2日。。。。。，民陣會向遊行上訴委員會上訴。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑。。。。，坦言不樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EC2OSH2X34RN57O3GEIR4MQLQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEC2OSH2X34RN57O3GEIR4MQLQQ.jpg&h=9ebdf442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑子杰（左）昨到北角警署商討7.1遊行安排，事後指警方態度敷衍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰：歷來最敷衍<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n民陣與警方會面個半小時，岑會後表示，為防疫及遊行人士的健康，民陣提出七個方案，包括保持1.5米社交距離，又提出分時段、分多個集合點出發，亦建議將六條行車線以三線梅花間竹地讓遊行人士通過等。他形容警方態度敷衍：「我哋發表意見嗰陣，警方筆記都冇做，『你講完啦？咁我哋完會』，並冇回應係咪採納，係我經歷過最敷衍嘅一次，感覺警方唔發不反對通知書機率應該係100%。」他續稱，警方代表只問了舉辦遊行集會期間如何保障市民健康，岑要求警方提出準則，若要求合理民陣願意跟從，但警方指主辦單位有責任確保公眾人士安全，警方沒有需要說明。岑斥警方說法荒謬，指港人擁有遊行集會權利，根據《公安條例》，警方有責任協助市民履行該權利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4W4UWQIMGERVJLW4BYYI3N7II.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4W4UWQIMGERVJLW4BYYI3N7II.gif&h=3089ed59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方不肯落實再度會談<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰又指，民陣申請7.1遊行終點是立法會添美道，由於該處佈滿水馬，若警方認為不適合，民陣可將終點改為中環，但警方沒有要求修訂。他又要求第二次會面繼續商討安排，警方僅稱「𠵱家答你唔到」。岑炮轟警方藉疫情打壓遊行集會，如給予一個假密碼鎖讓人撞密碼，「一定唔會撞到」。他表示，若警方反對7.1遊行，民陣會向遊行上訴委員會提出上訴，若失敗會再公布其他安排。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人稱，早前接獲一個團體通知，擬於7月1日在港島區舉行公眾活動，警方正處理有關通知。警方又稱尊重市民和平表達意見的權利，處理每宗公眾活動通知時，均會獨立評估風險。"},{"pid":"eceab38a64858425ef99c29f0ceec760e77ad10b","tid":2077123,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"反正唔預班狗會批<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013cb1c1aff6d23b1b6b947976fc770982ba85c6","tid":2077123,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"班狗只係垃圾"},{"pid":"6e0b8b31f9bafb3d33d774eecc9cb5019f5ef0d2","tid":2077123,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"7.1齊上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ddb502b8c4e588e1b16fa5a08a9992e757d6b6","tid":2077123,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"方案7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e0ceb8f7155d7c1f71a5a00c423f0baa13056e","tid":2077123,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"係咁，好似辯論比賽揾個反方支持正方。。你估會點"},{"pid":"364dd52a2ed8abfe13faae26bf037c19b9d36e9a","tid":2077123,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"777: 港人遊行權利沒損<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ccc75bd714dd02ce8b7cb7a0dc4adb53a39cfd","tid":2077123,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"洗9你批咩早知1/7一定出街行"},{"pid":"9254880d7ae0b7bdcd49a323c387059f88256534","tid":2077123,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"做樣都費事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e7f91c6625bdf639864dba00369a51a4a0057e","tid":2077123,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"564293b7c916110c542d645fd34c70fdeca547a3","tid":2077123,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"清算加制裁啦"}]}